item.title: S14 | E8 Neptune Launch, Million-Dollar Violin, Disaster Rebuilds & Perfect Egg Secrets
item.description:
The hosts talk about potential redevelopment plans in areas where wildfires and conflict destruction happened, the methods to a perfectly boiled egg, an upcoming social media platform known as Neptune in the works as well as a valuable violin being auctioned for millions of dollars amongst other things. *most, if not all of what’s been said is entirely satirical and has no intention of being taken as factual/legitimate sources or criticisms*
